               <p>THIRD DAY. - SATURDAY, JULY 14.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury - Before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>1380. 
               <persName id="t18270712-34-defend280" type="defendantName">
                  CATHERINE 
                  LYONS
               <interp inst="t18270712-34-defend280" type="surname" value="LYONS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270712-34-defend280" type="given" value="CATHERINE"></interp>
